This shouldn't be specified. The responses are of format:

  {
      "resource_filters": [
          {
              "resource": "resource_1",
              "filters": ["filter1", "filter2", "filter3"]
          }
      ]
  }

You'll note you have configured 'resources_key' above. That means openstacksdk will automatically unpack this for you, essentially doing something like:

  resource = resource[$resources_key]

So drop this line. It's not necessary

